{"id":63,"parent_id":48,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":63,"title":"Luke 15","subtitle":"","short_title":"Luke","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 15"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus gives the parables of the lost sheep, the piece of silver, and the prodigal son."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.1","order":"03.05.015.7749"},["b","1"],"Then drew near unto him all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"publicans"],"and sinners for to hear him."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.2","order":"03.05.015.7750"},["b","2"],"And the Pharisees and scribes murmured, saying, This man receiveth sinners, and eateth with them."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.3","order":"03.05.015.7751"},["b","3"],"¶And he spake this parable unto them, saying,"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.4","order":"03.05.015.7752"},["b","4"],"What man of you, having an hundred sheep, if he lose one of them, doth not leave the ninety and nine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"in"],"the wilderness, and go after that which is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"lost"],", until he find it?"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.5","order":"03.05.015.7753"},["b","5"],"And when he hath found",["i","it,"],"he layeth",["i","it"],"on his shoulders, rejoicing."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.6","order":"03.05.015.7754"},["b","6"],"And when he cometh home, he calleth together",["i","his"],"friends and neighbours, saying unto them, Rejoice with me; for I have found my sheep which was lost."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.7","order":"03.05.015.7755"},["b","7"],"I say unto you, that likewise",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"joy"],"shall be in heaven over one",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"sinner"],"that",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"repenteth"],", more than over ninety and nine just persons, which need no repentance."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.8","order":"03.05.015.7756"},["b","8"],"¶Either what woman having ten pieces of silver, if she lose one",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"piece"],", doth not light a candle, and sweep the house, and seek diligently till she find",["i","it?"]],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.9","order":"03.05.015.7757"},["b","9"],"And when she hath found",["i","it,"],"she calleth",["i","her"],"friends and",["i","her"],"neighbours together, saying, Rejoice with me; for I have found the piece which I had lost."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.10","order":"03.05.015.7758"},["b","10"],"Likewise, I say unto you, there is joy in the presence of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"angels"],"of God over one",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"sinner"],"that repenteth."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.11","order":"03.05.015.7759"},["b","11"],"¶And he said, A certain man had two sons:"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.12","order":"03.05.015.7760"},["b","12"],"And the younger of them said to",["i","his"],"father, Father, give me the portion of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"goods"],"that falleth",["i","to me."],"And he divided unto them",["i","his"],"living."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.13","order":"03.05.015.7761"},["b","13"],"And not many days after the younger son gathered all together, and took his journey into a far country, and there",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"wasted"],"his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"substance"],"with",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"riotous"],"living."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.14","order":"03.05.015.7762"},["b","14"],"And when he had spent all, there arose a mighty famine in that land; and he began to be in want."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.15","order":"03.05.015.7763"},["b","15"],"And he went and joined himself to a citizen of that country; and he sent him into his fields to feed swine."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.16","order":"03.05.015.7764"},["b","16"],"And he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"would fain"],"have filled his belly with the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"husks"],"that the swine did eat: and no man gave unto him."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.17","order":"03.05.015.7765"},["b","17"],"And when he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"came"],"to himself, he said, How many hired servants of my father’s have bread enough and to spare, and I perish with hunger!"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.18","order":"03.05.015.7766"},["b","18"],"I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"arise"],"and go to my father, and will say unto him, Father, I have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"sinned"],"against heaven, and before thee,"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.19","order":"03.05.015.7767"},["b","19"],"And am no more worthy to be called thy son: make me as one of thy hired servants."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.20","order":"03.05.015.7768"},["b","20"],"And he arose, and came to his father. But when he was yet a great way off, his father saw him, and had",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"compassion"],", and ran, and fell on his neck, and kissed him."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.21","order":"03.05.015.7769"},["b","21"],"And the son said unto him, Father, I have sinned against heaven, and in thy sight, and am no more",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"worthy"],"to be called thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"son"],"."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.22","order":"03.05.015.7770"},["b","22"],"But the father said to his servants, Bring forth the best robe, and put",["i","it"],"on him; and put a ring on his hand, and shoes on",["i","his"],"feet:"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.23","order":"03.05.015.7771"},["b","23"],"And bring hither the fatted calf, and kill",["i","it;"],"and let us eat, and be merry:"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.24","order":"03.05.015.7772"},["b","24"],"For this my son was dead, and is alive again; he was lost, and is found. And they began to be merry."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.25","order":"03.05.015.7773"},["b","25"],"Now his elder son was in the field: and as he came and drew nigh to the house, he heard musick and dancing."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.26","order":"03.05.015.7774"},["b","26"],"And he called one of the servants, and asked what these things meant."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.27","order":"03.05.015.7775"},["b","27"],"And he said unto him, Thy brother is come; and thy father hath killed the fatted calf, because he hath received him safe and sound."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.28","order":"03.05.015.7776"},["b","28"],"And he was angry, and would not go in: therefore came his father out, and entreated him."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.29","order":"03.05.015.7777"},["b","29"],"And he answering said to",["i","his"],"father, Lo, these many years do I serve thee, neither transgressed I at any time thy commandment: and yet thou never gavest me a kid, that I might make merry with my friends:"],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.30","order":"03.05.015.7778"},["b","30"],"But as soon as this thy son was come, which hath devoured thy living with harlots, thou hast killed for him the fatted calf."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.31","order":"03.05.015.7779"},["b","31"],"And he said unto him,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"Son"],", thou art ever with me, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"all"],"that I have is thine."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.32","order":"03.05.015.7780"},["b","32"],"It was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"meet"],"that we should make merry, and be glad: for this thy brother was dead, and is alive again; and was lost, and is found."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.1a","order":"03.05.015.7781"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/2.16.15-16"},"Mark 2:16 (15–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.4a","order":"03.05.015.7783"},["b","4a"],["span.small","JST"],"Luke 15:4 …",["i","and go into"],"the wilderness after that which is lost …"],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.4b","order":"03.05.015.7785"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/34.16.11-12,16"},"Ezek. 34:16 (11–12, 16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.7a","order":"03.05.015.7787"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/joy"},"TG Joy"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.7b","order":"03.05.015.7789"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/missionary-work"},"TG Missionary Work"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.7c","order":"03.05.015.7791"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/repent"},"TG Repent"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.8a","order":"03.05.015.7793"},["b","8a"],["span.small","GR"],["span.translit",["span.emphasis","drachma"]],"(a silver coin equal to the Roman",["i","denarius"],"—a workman’s daily wage)."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.10a","order":"03.05.015.7795"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/angels"},"TG Angels"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.10b","order":"03.05.015.7797"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worth-of-souls"},"TG Worth of Souls"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.12a","order":"03.05.015.7799"},["b","12a"],["span.small","GR"],"property."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.13a","order":"03.05.015.7801"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/waste"},"TG Waste"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.13b","order":"03.05.015.7803"},["b","13b"],["span.small","GR"],"property."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.13c","order":"03.05.015.7805"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/28.7"},"Prov. 28:7"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/rioting-and-reveling"},"TG Rioting and Reveling"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.16a","order":"03.05.015.7807"},["b","16a"],["span.small","GR"],"desired, set the heart upon."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.16b","order":"03.05.015.7809"},["b","16b"],["span.small","GR"],"pods (of the carob tree)."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.17a","order":"03.05.015.7811"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/119.59"},"Ps. 119:59"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/repent"},"TG Repent"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.18a","order":"03.05.015.7813"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/3.40"},"Lam. 3:40"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.18b","order":"03.05.015.7815"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/confession"},"TG Confession"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.20a","order":"03.05.015.7817"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/benevolence"},"TG Benevolence"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/compassion"},"Compassion"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-love-within"},"Family, Love within"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mercy"},"Mercy"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.21a","order":"03.05.015.7819"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/contrite-heart"},"TG Contrite Heart"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worthiness"},"Worthiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.21b","order":"03.05.015.7821"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-patriarchal"},"TG Family, Patriarchal"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.31a","order":"03.05.015.7823"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-love-within"},"TG Family, Love within"],"."],["div",{"id":"31b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.31b","order":"03.05.015.7825"},["b","31b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.38"},"D&C 84:38"],"."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/15.32a","order":"03.05.015.7827"},["b","32a"],["span.small","GR"],"necessary."]]}
